org.afplib.afplib

Interface IDD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IDDImpl

    public interface IDD
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'IDD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • UNITBASE
    • XRESOL
    • YRESOL
    • XSIZE
    • YSIZE
    • SDFS

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getIDD()
